-on-the-us-elections-fuck-donald-trump-3804542">乔尼·米切尔</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-slams-those-avoiding-presidential-election-what-the-fuck-are-you-talking-about-3790934">梅根·西·斯塔林</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cher-endorses-kamala-harris-im-so-grateful-to-be-able-to-make-my-voice-count-this-year-3804267">雪儿</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-speaks-at-kamala-harris-rally-hits-out-at-donald-trumps-comments-about-detroit-3804404">利佐</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/obama-raps-lose-yourself-verse-at-kamala-harris-rally-after-being-introduced-by-eminem-3805325">阿姆</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/usher-joins-kamala-harris-at-atlanta-rally-everything-we-do-in-the-next-17-days-will-affect-our-children-and-grandchildren-3804493">亚瑟小子</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pnk-perform-what-about-us-with-daughter-to-close-democratic-national-convention-3786178">P!nk</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/leonardo-dicaprio">莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/leonardo-dicaprio-and-bad-bunny-have-endorsed-kamala-harris-3806836">Bad Bunny</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bon-iver-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-in-wisconsin-3781912">Bon Iver</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/quavo-backs-kamala-harris-for-tackling-gun-violence-at-atlanta-rally-3779672">Quavo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-mumford-sons-push-for-voting-plan-as-they-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-3808418">Mumford &amp; Sons</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/these-are-glorillas-four-reasons-to-vote-for-kamala-harris-3807830">GloRilla</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/evanescence">Evanence</a>的 Amy Lee 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Finneas">Finneas。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bruce-springsteen-perform-his-biggest-hits-at-kamala-harris-rally-3806094">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀最近参加了亚特兰大的哈里斯集会</a>，而九月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-for-president-3792514">泰勒·斯威夫特写道，她也将投票给现任副总统</a>，“因为她为权利和事业而战，我认为需要一位战士来捍卫它们”。</p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad1 id_ad_content-horiz-center"><p>本周早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/avengers-cast-reunite-to-endorse-kamala-harris-kamala-forever-3808508">包括马克·鲁法洛、斯嘉丽·约翰逊、小罗伯特·唐尼、克里斯·埃文斯和唐·钱德尔在内的漫威《<i>复仇者联盟》</i>演员阵容</a>在 Instagram 视频中重聚，为哈里斯背书。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/arnold-schwarzenegger-voices-support-for-kamala-harris-as-a-former-republican-governor-3808452">加州前共和党州长阿诺·施瓦辛格也表示，他将投票给哈里斯</a>。 “在成为共和党人之前，我永远是美国人，”他说。 “这就是为什么本周我投票给卡马拉·哈里斯和蒂姆·沃尔兹。我与大家分享它，因为我认为你们中有很多人和我有同样的感受。你不承认我们的国家。你生气是对的。”</p><p>特朗普的知名支持者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kid-rock-shares-his-thoughts-on-taylor-swift-and-eminem-endorsing-kamala-harris-3807296">摇滚小子（Kid Rock）</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/kelsey-grammer-banned-from-talking-about-trump-support-in-interviews-reporter-claims-3553743">凯尔西·格拉默（Kelsey Grammer）</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-makes-a-brief-appearance-at-donald-trump-supporters-rally-in-beverly-hills-3784869">坎耶·维斯特（Kanye West）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/hulk-hogan-asks-crowd-if-they-want-him-to-body-slam-kamala-harris-3786054">浩克·霍根（Hulk Hogan）</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3795532" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3795532" style="width: 1392px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3795532" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/StVincent-2024-credit-DavidWilliamBaum.jpg" alt="圣文森特西班牙专辑" width="1392" height="884" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/StVincent-2024-credit-DavidWilliamBaum.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/StVincent-2024-credit-DavidWilliamBaum-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/202